column1: You are a grandmaster. You will be given a partially completed game. After seeing it you should THINK and choose the best next move. Use standard algebraic notation.ALWAYS repeat the entire representation of the game so far. NEVER give a turn number. NEVER EXPLAIN YOUR CHOISE.THINK. WHITE TO PLAY. d4 d5 2. c4 Nf6 3.
